== Welcome to Alternetica.com
	the portal for cooperative company alternetica.com, 
	what about this site ?
	  front end
	  - several features for contents and organization from categories
	  - multilingual
	  - Picture gallery
	  - multi language
	  - Social Network
	  - separation of content by category
		
	  backend administration panel
	  - manage users
	  - manage contents & categories
	  - manage gallery 
          - manage blogs, posts  & comments
	  - manage Todo-list's, Calendars & Tasks
	
== step for install

		bundle install 
		rake db:create
		rake db:migration
...